items.name: Side Show
items.text: Film director Bill Condon (Gods and Monsters, Chicago, Kinsey, Dreamgirls) makes his Broadway debut with this musical, which follows the Hilton twins (Daisy and Violet) through the world of show business in the 1920s and '30s.
